        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2009-06-22 14:52:24   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1245711144303279999" id="quote-1245711144303279999" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1245711144303279999" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=124522844824185623&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1245711144303279999&amp;page=2" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> 
