        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2009-06-23 07:51:16   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1245772276291559572" id="quote-1245772276291559572" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1245772276291559572" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=21&amp;mid=124522844824185623&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1245772276291559572&amp;page=2" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> 
