        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Guru" href="/users/isyris">Lady isyris</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Guru">Guru</div></div><div class="msgAvatar"><img alt="Avatar" height="120" width="120" src="http://common.allakhazam.com/images/d/0/d00925a85e9a25a311a5f0442e234f5f.png"/></div><div class="msgStar"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/></div><div class="msgWhoNum">2,534 posts</div>
